title: Ft Lauderdale Luxury Limo
name: Ft Lauderdale Luxury Limo
description:
Ft Lauderdale Luxury Limo is a provider of Miami Florida, Fort Lauderdale Florida, and Palm Beach Florida area Limousine services and transportation. Our high quality services are available in Dade, West Palm Beach and Broward counties.

Ft Lauderdale Luxury Limo is an established and trusted ground transportation service, with client references available upon request. Our fleet consists of limousines, vans, luxury sedans and more. Ft Lauderdale Luxury Limo is licensed and insured and established as a corporation. With official permits to provide car service and limousine service throughout the area for local pickups as well as to and from airports. We are also recognized as a transportation option to and from Port of Miami, Port Everglades and the Port of Palm Beach.

Give us a call or get an online quote. We assure you that you will get where you are going on time, stress free and in style with our limousine services.
